Name: CatCatch
About the game: In the Arkanoid game CatCatch you have to find out all cats in the room. Use your high tech Ball to clear obstacles.Just like toys, chairs, a cup of coffee, or anythings in the room. Pay attention to the falling items. It can be helpful or useless.
